.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/research.md:224:### 3.2 The five-stage funnel (scoring backbone + bottleneck localizer + remediation router, one structure)
