.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/research.md:342:*End of consolidated report. Source: 20 iterations × 4 models (MiniMax-2.7, DeepSeek-v4-pro, GPT-5.5, Opus); MiniMax iter-002 empty. All cross-model attributions and carried `[SOURCE: …]` citations preserved inline.*
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md:2:name: deep-agent-improvement
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md:4:allowed-tools: [Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep]
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md:7:  - deep-agent-improvement
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md:13:  - model-benchmark mode
