.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:127:### Release Readiness Rule
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:137:This section records wave planning for the canonical Skill Advisor manual test package. The scenario corpus is large enough to split across operators while keeping category ownership clear.
