.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/changelog/v0.2.0.md:63:  - skill-advisor `@spec-kit/*` workspace-alias imports (excludes `@spec-kit/shared/embeddings/*`, the single documented exception)
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/changelog/v0.2.0.md:71:- `mcp_server/tsconfig.json`: `rootDir: "."` removed, the alias resolution to `system-spec-kit/shared/embeddings/factory.js` lies outside the previous rootDir constraint. Removing it lets tsc walk the workspace boundary cleanly.
