.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/graph/skill_graph_query_cookbook.md:73:  "skillId": "system-skill-advisor",
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/graph/skill_graph_query_cookbook.md:78:**Worked example**: `system-skill-advisor` currently has no hard dependencies. Query returns an empty edge list from the source graph-metadata.json.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/graph/skill_graph_query_cookbook.md:120:{ "queryType": "enhances", "skillId": "system-skill-advisor" }
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/graph/skill_graph_query_cookbook.md:128:  "skillId": "system-skill-advisor",
