.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/decisions/deferred_decisions.md:127:A future packet (`006-skill-advisor/010-old-hooks-helper-migration` or similar) should migrate the helpers to NEW before they can be removed from OLD. That packet is separate from F6 and is NOT bounded by the 2026-08-16 date.
