   182	
   183	Mapped so Lane C reuses proven metrics rather than inventing them. **Coverage caveat for model comparison:** DeepSeek and GPT-5.5 had live web access and actually fetched sources; **Opus's web was permission-gated** so all its citations are flagged `[web-unverified]` (drawn from established knowledge, recommended for later confirmation) `[opus/i1 web-note]`; MiniMax cited a mix.
