.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/README.md:75:| `run-benchmark.cjs` | Loads a profile, scores fixture outputs, writes `report.json` plus an immutable history snapshot, and appends a `benchmark_run` row to the state log. Sanitizes `fixture.id` and bounds authored regex patterns. |
