.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/scoring/validation_baselines.md:63:`advisor_validate` is a heavy operation. It runs the full corpus plus holdout plus parity plus safety plus latency slices in one pass. Require `confirmHeavyRun=true` to invoke.
