.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py:2622:            conf_threshold=conf_threshold,
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py:2623:            uncert_threshold=uncert_threshold,
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py:2627:def apply_confidence_calibration(recommendations: List[Dict[str, Any]]) -> None:
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py:2628:    """Adjust confidence using score margin and ambiguity pressure."""
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py:2639:        confidence = recommendation["confidence"]
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py:2652:        calibrated = confidence - margin_penalty - ambiguity_penalty + evidence_bonus
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py:2653:        recommendation["confidence"] = round(max(0.0, min(0.95, calibrated)), 2)
