.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py:2668:        recommendation["confidence"] = round(recommendation["confidence"] * 0.90, 2)
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py:2669:        recommendation["uncertainty"] = round(max(0.0, recommendation["uncertainty"] * 0.85), 2)
